4. Prompt engineering templates for question generation
5. Sample code (Python preferred) for the core engine
6. Tech stack recommendations with cost estimates
7. Implementation roadmap with timelines
8. Security and content moderation considerations
9. Scalability planning for thousands of concurrent users

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

