• Math must be 100% accurate — include validation steps
• Content must be age-appropriate (8-18+ range)
• System must handle 1000+ concurrent competition matches
• Questions should feel exciting, not like traditional school tests
• The "boxing ring / punch box" theme must be consistent throughout
• Platform must work on web and mobile

